    "description": "Wishlist and follow, if you're interested in Cracked<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130750/extras/37355c6ac7b0e7743a953a46701ba84c.poster.avif?t=1698309103\" width=414 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130750/extras/37355c6ac7b0e7743a953a46701ba84c.webm?t=1698309103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130750/extras/37355c6ac7b0e7743a953a46701ba84c.mp4?t=1698309103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Cracked</strong> is a difficult 2D Platformer. Dominate the leaderboards by completing the maps as fast as possible. Explore the abandoned Factory.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE VARIOUS LOCATIONS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>From all the locations, you can choose which one to explore first.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130750/extras/b414768639786cc4f548b1970223b930.avif?t=1698309103\" width=640 height=134 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CUSTOMIZE YOUR CHARACTER</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>It's up to you how you want to customize your character.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130750/extras/112b255277ce9b957dea99101b84ef8c.avif?t=1698309103\" width=640 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DOMINATE THE LEADERBOARDS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Finish the maps as fast as you can and put your name on the leaderboard.<br></li><li>You can either compete against your own personal best, your friends or the world.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130750/extras/a24dc5343a0945b7846d1bb2edd5faa0.avif?t=1698309103\" width=640 height=140 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEFEAT THE BOSS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Save your friends by defeating the boss in every campaign's last map, and unlock them as a playable character.<br></li><li>It's your choice who you think is worthy of being saved first.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130750/extras/764403c78db2651802648e1ba7c51667.avif?t=1698309103\" width=640 height=101 /></span><br><br>",
